title: Alice in Wonderland Jumperskirt
description:
Alice in Wonderland Costume Lolita Jumper Dress High Waisted Skirt with Straps Fairytale Adult Halloween Lewis Carrol Petite to Plus size

This Alice in Wonderland Jumper is a variation of our classic Jumper but is created from a robin's egg blue cotton with a embroidered wonderland pocket. It is inspired by book through the looking glass. Don't fall down the rabbit hole! Can be made in Petite and Plus sizes.

This outfit is great for parties, Halloween and costume events, it's so comfy to wear! It can even be a fun conversational outfit you wear out and about!

This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waist for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with a two black button in the back.

***Want the whole look!!! Follow listing below for petticoat, blouse
https://www.etsy.com/listing/75359146/lolita-vicotiran-blouse-white-kona?ref=shop_home_active_9
https://www.etsy.com/listing/220108893/white-cotton-lolita-petticoat-western?ref=shop_home_active_13
OPTIONS
Embroidery can be
Eat me http://www.urbanthreads.com/products.aspx?productid=UT2841
Drink me http://www.urbanthreads.com/products.aspx?productid=UT2885
Cheshire cat! http://www.urbanthreads.com/products.aspx?productid=UT3312
All embroidery designs from Urban Threads!

Make time:
Takes about 3-4 weeks to be made and then is shipped Priority mail domestic which takes about 2-3 days and priority international which takes 6-10 days but can vary up to a month depending on the country. Shipping Upgrade available message us for details.

Washing:
Machine wash and hang to dry.

============================
Sizes include in message to the seller

Small-Waist 25-29
Medium-Waist 30-34
Large-Waist 35-39
XL-Waist 40-42
XXL-Waist 43-45
3X Waist 46-48
4X Waist 49-51
5X 52-54
Can also be made in child sizes for -$15 less.

MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

Hangs about 22 inches can be made shorter or up to 24 inches longs, measure from your waist to where you would like the bottom of the jumper to be.

How to Measure:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=81vN7EZ6tK4&list=UUFYdAx68FcajKytbzZ1r1gA&index=1&feature=plcp
============================

If you have any questions just message or e-mail me at kmkmcclain [at] gmail.com

Mode Lily Smith
Photos by Jen Montgomery Photography

Handmade by KMK Designs in Minnesota. Item ships directly from vendor.

content:
Alice in Wonderland Costume Lolita Jumper Dress High Waisted Skirt with Straps Fairytale Adult Halloween Lewis Carrol Petite to Plus size

This Alice in Wonderland Jumper is a variation of our classic Jumper but is created from a robin's egg blue cotton with a embroidered wonderland pocket. It is inspired by book through the looking glass. Don't fall down the rabbit hole! Can be made in Petite and Plus sizes.

This outfit is great for parties, Halloween and costume events, it's so comfy to wear! It can even be a fun conversational outfit you wear out and about!

This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waist for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with a two black button in the back.

***Want the whole look!!! Follow listing below for petticoat, blouse
https://www.etsy.com/listing/75359146/lolita-vicotiran-blouse-white-kona?ref=shop_home_active_9
https://www.etsy.com/listing/220108893/white-cotton-lolita-petticoat-western?ref=shop_home_active_13
OPTIONS
Embroidery can be
Eat me http://www.urbanthreads.com/products.aspx?productid=UT2841
Drink me http://www.urbanthreads.com/products.aspx?productid=UT2885
Cheshire cat! http://www.urbanthreads.com/products.aspx?productid=UT3312
All embroidery designs from Urban Threads!

Make time:
Takes about 3-4 weeks to be made and then is shipped Priority mail domestic which takes about 2-3 days and priority international which takes 6-10 days but can vary up to a month depending on the country. Shipping Upgrade available message us for details.

Washing:
Machine wash and hang to dry.

============================
Sizes include in message to the seller

Small-Waist 25-29
Medium-Waist 30-34
Large-Waist 35-39
XL-Waist 40-42
XXL-Waist 43-45
3X Waist 46-48
4X Waist 49-51
5X 52-54
Can also be made in child sizes for -$15 less.

MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

Hangs about 22 inches can be made shorter or up to 24 inches longs, measure from your waist to where you would like the bottom of the jumper to be.

How to Measure:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=81vN7EZ6tK4&list=UUFYdAx68FcajKytbzZ1r1gA&index=1&feature=plcp
============================

If you have any questions just message or e-mail me at kmkmcclain [at] gmail.com

Mode Lily Smith
Photos by Jen Montgomery Photography

Cultivate soft feelings with the Alice Ruffle Bloomers with Bunny Lace from Mist. These cute little bloomers are just full of ruffles down to the bottom of the shorts. Welcome to Café Sumire a place full of roses, tea and music.

This listing is for the purchase of one Happy Tartans ♪✮ Long Sleeve Blouse in blue.

Happy Tartans ♪✮ is a collection inspired by japan kawaii nostalgia: lolita early days and the femenine urge for being Marie Antoinette while living in a modern small town.

 

G A R M E N T · I N F O

✮ Blouse is made by tartan fabric we have completely produced in Barcelona. This tartan is exclusive by Violet Fane and Sumire, as we have personally dyed the treads to be the exact bright 80s colors we wanted for the collection.

✮ ALL laces and buttons are as well produced and made in Spain.

✮ Fabric and lace is made by cotton.

✮ Blouse is fully elastic and wide back /tall friendly.

✮ It has an embroidery Sumire logo.

title: Blue Meadow Dress
description:
The meadow dress is inspired by wildflowers scattered across an open field.  It has a flattering scoop neckline, an elastic waist, and pockets! 

This dress is elegant without being overly formal. It has vintage class, but is made entirely from comfortable, breathable cotton - including the lining! And of course, the pockets are very practical for any outing.

The waistband and sleeve cuffs are made with elastic for a soft and flattering fit. Designed with versatility in mind, the waist cinches and stretches to match your shape. The buttons running up the center front of the dress are decorative only, so they will not gape open. Wear it with or without a petticoat for your desired silhouette. This dress is photographed with a petticoat (not included).

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: 100% cotton. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang to dry

 

Size Chart

 Size Chest Waist
XS 31"-34" 26"-30"
S 34"-36" 30"-34"
M 36"-38" 34"-36"
L 38"-42" 36"-42"
1X 42"-44" 40"-46"
2X 44"-48" 44"-50"
3X 48"-54" 48"-54"
4X 52"-56" 52"-58"

These measurements are recommended body measurements. Choose the size closest to your actual measurements. The actual garment is slightly larger to account for wearing ease. This waistband is elastic and can accommodate a slightly larger size, and it can also be tied down to a smaller size. All measurements in inches.

This item is made by Atelier Heidi in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Celestial Princess Dress
description:
Black Chiffon Dress Witchy Clothing Witch Costume Halloween Sheer Goth Dress Gothic Clothing Custom to Petite to Plus Size

This black chiffon dress could be a costume or your next fancy outfit for formal events. Comfy and flowy and perfect for that inner witch.

-This style is called the "Celestial Princess" part of our Collection Celestial Punk and is made locally in St. Paul.


MAKE TIME:
Takes about 2-3 weeks to be made and sent to you. Ships Priority mail domestic 2-3 days and international which takes 1-6 weeks


Washing:
Can be washed gentle cycle in the washer and then hang to dry
________________________________

SIZES**

XSmall
Waist 22-24
Bust 29-31

Small
waist 25-29
bust 32-35

Medium
waist 30-35
bust 36-40

Large
waist 36-40
bust 41-45

XL
waist 41-44
bust 46-50

For plus size orders (anything above a 45 waist), we do orders custom to your measurements.



MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store
-Bust:
When measuring, measure around the fullest part of the bust, over the nipple and around the back keeping the tape even.
Please also include your cup size.

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

Waist to floor for hem

How to Measure:
Basic:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kziKXUzxNSE

Advanced:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6eXvD7FfDE

Convo us or e-mail us at kmkmcclain@gmail.com with any questions.

title: Cherry Tea Apron Skirt
description:
Is that the kettle whistle?

This Cherry Tea Apron Skirt from Hard Candy is ready for the party. A treat for the eyes, it features ruffled top with lovely embroidered cherries and flowers. Continuing down the skirt is two heart shaped pockets and a lovely lace trim lining the bottom half. This would be lovely to wear as a main piece or paired with another for layering.

Details

title: Chiffon Ombre Wedding Dress
description:
Chiffon Ombre Wedding Dress with Sleeves Unique Simple Fairy Long Sleeve Colorful Gown Bridesmaid or Bride Petite to Plus size Custommade

This delicate chiffon ombre gown is the perfect wedding dress for a beach, traditional or bohemian theme. It is simple enough to be worn as a elegant day dress or works for bridesmaids, get them in all different ombre to accent your wedding colors.
Has a long sleeve that stops just below the elbow, length to be made to hit the floor. The front ruffle covers a hidden zipper that makes the gown easy to stay on and gets rid of any button gaping problem.
The back has lacing to help with sizing without an in person fitting. Waist and wrist also have hidden elastic to make the fit snug yet comfortable.
Comes with lovely ribbon sash in the last color of the ombre.

Style is called "Sunset Dress" locally made in St. Paul, MN

***The top part is sheer, but can be made opaque, the bottom skirt comes with a lining but can also be made without.

Made from a soft chiffon that feels soft and silky against your skin. Sheer enough to be seductive, but opaque enough to still be classy. Buttons up in front,
has a more loose fit then our other dresses. Sewn with lovely french seams.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

MAKE TIME:
Takes about 6-8 weeks to make then is sent to you via priority mail for domestic shipments which takes 2-3 days and international which takes 1-6 weeks depending on time of year and country, message us for shipping upgrades.
-------------------------------
WASHING:
Dry Clean Only

SIZES:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
We can either do custom to your measurement or you can ask for a size below

XSmall
Waist 22-24
Bust 29-31

Small
waist 25-29
bust 32-35

Medium
waist 30-35
bust 36-40

Large
waist 36-40
bust 41-45

XL
waist 41-44
bust 46-50

For plus size orders (anything above a 45 waist), we do orders custom to your measurements.
Please follow description below for measurements.

MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store
-Bust:
When measuring, measure around the fullest part of the bust, over the nipple and around the back keeping the tape even.
Please also include your cup size.

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

How to Measure:
Basic:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kziKXUzxNSE

Advanced:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6eXvD7FfDE

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


If you have questions please message us here or email us at kmkmcclain [at] gmail.com


Photo by Jen Montgomery and Photosynthetique
Model Davika Serene and Andrea Acosta

Handmade by KMK Designs in Minnesota. Item ships directly from vendor.

Has a long sleeve that stops just below the elbow, length to be made to hit the floor. The front ruffle covers a hidden zipper that makes the gown easy to stay on and gets rid of any button gaping problem.
The back has lacing to help with sizing without an in person fitting. Waist and wrist also have hidden elastic to make the fit snug yet comfortable.
Comes with lovely ribbon sash in the last color of the ombre.

Style is called "Sunset Dress" locally made in St. Paul, MN

***The top part is sheer, but can be made opaque, the bottom skirt comes with a lining but can also be made without.

Made from a soft chiffon that feels soft and silky against your skin. Sheer enough to be seductive, but opaque enough to still be classy. Buttons up in front,
has a more loose fit then our other dresses. Sewn with lovely french seams.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

MAKE TIME:
Takes about 6-8 weeks to make then is sent to you via priority mail for domestic shipments which takes 2-3 days and international which takes 1-6 weeks depending on time of year and country, message us for shipping upgrades.
-------------------------------
WASHING:
Dry Clean Only

SIZES:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
We can either do custom to your measurement or you can ask for a size below

XSmall
Waist 22-24
Bust 29-31

Small
waist 25-29
bust 32-35

Medium
waist 30-35
bust 36-40

Large
waist 36-40
bust 41-45

XL
waist 41-44
bust 46-50

For plus size orders (anything above a 45 waist), we do orders custom to your measurements.
Please follow description below for measurements.

MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store
-Bust:
When measuring, measure around the fullest part of the bust, over the nipple and around the back keeping the tape even.
Please also include your cup size.

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

title: Cora Skirt
description:
An elegant, full-bodied skirt made from 100% cotton! It has two layers: an outer layer with dramatic lace cutouts, and a solid lining layer that provides full coverage underneath. Both layers are cotton, which makes this skirt very comfortable and breathable.

The waistband is elastic, making the fit stretchy and accommodating. It also has pockets at both side seams!

These photos show the skirt over a petticoat to show off the full volume. You can also wear it without a petticoat for a softer, more casual silhouette. 

Perfect for dressing up in an elegant Lolita coordinate, or layering with neutral pieces for a gentler mori kei vibe. 

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: 100% cotton. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold on gentle cycle, tumble dry low or hang to dry

 

Colors

Color can be difficult to capture perfectly in photographs, and your screen may display colors differently than they appear in real life. To help you best visualize the final color, these are the exact Pantone shades use to formulate the fabric dye:

Cream: Pantone 11-0809 TCX Ecru
Vintage Rose: Pantone 17-1512 TPG Nostalgia Rose

Luxurious Linen Blend

This versatile fall blouse is an excellent addition to any wardrobe. It features raglan sleeves that are gathered at the wrist with elastic, and a high collar trimmed with a lace edged ruffle.

  • Lace trim

title: Daydream Crop Sweater
description:
Cozy up this spring with your favorite dreamy jumper~!✨

Each pastel sweater features a velvet-like star and rainbow applique accompanied by fluffy chenille clouds⛅️ On the back is Precious Bbyz embroidered across the shoulders.

Sweaters are 100% cotton with a soft lightweight knit and big bold embroidery. Featuring balloon sleeves, dropped shoulders, and a boxy cropped bodice, this sweater is perfect for a variety of high-waisted trousers, skirts, and shorts.

title: Deer Dress
description:
The Deer Dress is a dreamy fawn design, made of custom-printed velveteen to mimic the texture of a deer's fur. Featuring embroidered antlers on a Peter Pan collar, a removable waist bow which can be positioned in any direction, and pockets. The contrast sleeves have beautiful embroidered details and a lace inset.

A long row of functional buttons creates the center front opening, lined with lace. These buttons are placed closely together to prevent gaping. The velveteen body, contrast sleeves, decorative lace, and lining are all 100% cotton.

title: Egg Cardigan
description:
It’s always sweater weather when you have body dysmorphia! Okay but let’s be real, these cardigans are designed to be a hug just like from a comfy knit blanket. Each cardigan is designed to be as sensory friendly as possible. The material is made from 100% Cotton that is hand dyed to match the designated color. Both the material and that the knit is heavier than average is designed to help anyone with sensory issues. But the most important part is that all tags are in the front left pocket to avoid any unnecessary tag contact. Don’t be surprised if your friends or partner(s) want to borrow it since it’s just so cozy. 

This cardi can be the perfect addition to your wardrobe! It can be worn both super every day outfits, or dressed up with the perfect collared blouse, skirt or whatever you plan to coord it with! 

The Carigans are available in 5 sizes: XS, Small-medium, Large-XL, 2XL-3XL, 4XL-5XL. Each size is designed to fit loose or oversized with the following US Standard measurements. They are also designed with longer than average arm length to accommodate taller folks (yay!)

    ***Note about sizing: after initial production we received feedback stating that the 4/6XL is not true to size to fit a 6XL. Going forward all marketing of this size will state 4/5XL, however the tag still indicates “6XL”. The measurements are still the same, we are just no longer marketing this size as 6XL going forward***

note: models are wearing the 2/3XL 

 

This item is made by Egglien Creations in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Embroidered Mushroom Shorts
description:
Please use the size chart to determine the best size shorts for your body, don't trust your normal size! If any of your measurement is on the borderline between two sizes, it is suggested to size up. In the larger sizes (XL and above), the shorts tend to run smaller than standard US sizes. The size you most often wear may not align with the sizing of these shorts, so it is suggested to measure your body to find the best fit.

Life doesn’t always grant us the opportunity to joyfully frolic through the forest and forage for mushrooms, no matter how much we’d like to. 

But sometimes, life does show us ways we can remember to stay grounded- no matter how busy the day is.

So make sure to add these specially embroidered cottagecore shorts to your closet so you can: 

    • Embrace your inner fairy in olive green without even needing to be outside
    • Stay cute and comfortable in the loose-fitting high waisted shorts
    • Wear simply the stretchy waistband or finish the look with a belt
    • Show off some cute lil’ mushrooms that won’t fade or peel
    • Be comforted knowing these polyester shorts won’t shrink after washing

Orders will include slim black belt to go with the shorts!

Both Laci (white shirt) and Sarah (black shirt) are wearing a size large!

95% Polyester / 5% Spandex

This item is made by Sugar Lich in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

This comfy unisex hoodie has a soft outside with a vibrant print, and an even softer brushed fleece inside. The hoodie has a relaxed fit, and it's perfect for wrapping yourself into on a chilly evening. Made to order item, please allow 7-12 days to ship.

• 70% polyester, 27% cotton, 3% elastane
• Fabric weight: 8.85 oz/yd² (300 g/m²)
• Soft cotton-feel fabric face
• Brushed fleece fabric inside
• Double-lined hood with design on both sides
• Unisex style
• Overlock seams
• Comes with drawstrings

title: Frill Yoke Onepiece Dress
description:
This is a dress adorned with many frills on the yoke.  There's a ribbon on the back for a seamless design, and the sleeves are also a minette-like point. A lining was not added, so you can enjoy the sheerness by wearing your favorite slip. The fabric is thin and light spun voile. It has a natural texture. The dress has a beautiful drape. 

Details:

  • Back button closure
  • Unlined
  • Material: 100% polyester

Measurements: 

  • [ Size M ]
  • Length: 118cm
  • Shoulder Width: 41cm
  • Sleeve Length: 54.5cm
  • Cuffs: 22cm

title: Ginza Kissaten Groovy Skirt
description:
✿ G I N Z A  K I S S A T E N ✿ Skirt ✿ Groovy Café

Ginza, Tokyo, 1978. We drink our melon soda while hearing romantic pop music in the old café; crowded by plants and groovy furniture.

title: Gothic Circus High Waisted Skirt
description:
Gothic Circus High Waisted Skirt Tim Burton Adult Halloween Costume Beetle Juice Dress Custom Made Petite to Plus Size

This Gothic Steampunk dress has a high low hem with a striped ruffle. This jumper has adjustable bustle pull in the front, take may it even more versatile and fun! This Gothic Jumper dress is great for an adult Halloween costume that you can work into your everyday wardrobe adding some gothy Tim Burton fun! Works for a witch circus look, a beetle juice inspired look or a Tim Burton inspired outfit!
This style is called out "Goth Ellis Jumper" .
This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waist for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with two buttons in the back.

WANT THE WHOLE LOOK?
**Black ruffle under dress is from a petticoat worn with the jumper
can be purchased here
https://www.etsy.com/listing/59005962/gothic-loltia-petticoat-pirate-steampunk?ref=shop_home_active_14
The dress sits under the bust. Top can be purchased here
https://www.etsy.com/listing/290352995/goth-lace-hooded-top-sheer-cowl-petite?ref=shop_home_active_5

MAKE TIME:
Will take up to 2-3 weeks in our schedule to make and ship to you. Shipped Priority which takes 2-3 days domestic and 1-6 weeks international varies by country.

For international please give yourself a 4 week delivery time on top of the make time. Some countries there is a faster delivery please inquire. There is also shipping upgrades available.

Washing:
Dry cleaned or hand washed
_______________________________
SIZES

Sizes Natural waist about an inch above your belly button
Small-Waist 25-29
Medium-Waist 30-34
Large-Waist 35-39
XL-Waist 40-42
XXL-Waist 43-45
XXL-Waist 43-45
3X Waist 46-48
4X Waist 49-51
5X 52-54

Length is about 22-24 inches from your waist please include a specific length from your waist if you have a preference.

Meant to be worn with a petticoat, but can be worn without. Can't be worn without a blouse.

How to Measure:
Basic:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kziKXUzxNSE

Advanced:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6eXvD7FfDE

-------------------------

Please message us with any questions at info [!at] kmkdesigns.org



Photos by CC Photo Arts
Model Leslie Barlow
Hair by Rachel Reyna
Make-up Fearless Cosmetics

Designed by KMK Designs in Minnesota, USA. Item ships directly from vendor.

This style is called out "Goth Ellis Jumper" .
This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waist for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with two buttons in the back.

Details

✮ Apron is made by tartan fabric we have completely produced in Barcelona. This tartan is exclusive by Violet Fane and Sumire, as we have personally dyied the treads to be the exact bright 80s colors we wanted for the collection.

title: Instant Shipping! Candy Shoppe Over The Knee Socks
description:
Sweet & bitter twists.

 

The Candy Shoppe OTKs feature a scalloped cuff and come in two sizes at over-the-knee length.

Size 1 measures 52-55cm in length from the heel (3cm margin of error due to the manufacturing process) and stretches to max 20 inches around the calf.

Size 2 measures 52-55cm in length from the heel (3cm margin of error due to the manufacturing process) and stretches to max 27 inches around the calf.

Fits most US Adult shoe sizes.

Photos may not be representative of the real product color due to differences in screen monitors.

Because of the dyeing process, color threads may vary among socks.

Due to the elasticity combined with the woven nature of the socks, pilling is normal where color threads change.

Wash inside out in cold water inside a delicate garment bag or hand-wash.

 This item is made by Dandy Puppeteer in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Jewelry Box Onepiece Dress
description:
Admire these sparkling jewels within our favorite jewelry box collection. Sparkle and excitement are captured in the Jewelry box series.

This is a square-neck dress bordered with wide tulle lace. The gorgeous square neckline beautifully accentuates the neck. The ruffles on the chest and skirt add a delicate touch of sweetness. The waist has a ribbon front and an elastic back, so you can wear it in your preferred size.

The print is applied to domestically produced slub shantung fabric, which features irregular horizontal stripes visible on the surface. It is soft to the touch. The lining of the upper body is made of a cool lining, which is absorbent and quick-drying.

Details:

  • Zipper back closure
  • Elastic cuffs
  • Pocket on right side
  • Inside is lined
  • Outer material: 100% polyester
  • Lining: 100% polyester

title: Juicy Grape Onepiece Dress
description:
This is an original fabric with a painting-like soft depiction of fragrant grapes. Ribbons are added to the ripe fruit for a lovely look.

It's a yoke switch made of diamond tulle overlaid with lace gives this dress a ladylike impression, and it is decorated with round pearl buttons reminiscent of grapes. The puff sleeves with a switch at the top create a soft and lovely silhouette. Elastic at the back waist makes it comfortable to wear.

The irregular surface texture gives it a full, puffy look, and the ring pear texture is soft to the touch. It has a drape and an elegant feel.

title: Jumperskirt - Mots Doux à ma Chérie
description:
Mots Doux à ma Chérie is our collection for true romantics that combines shōwa era manga style, vintage Valentine's aesthetics, and a sakura theme, resulting in a sweet-as-candy romantic retro print.

Whether you are going on a Valentine's day date, having a cherry blossom picnic or simply feeling all lovey-dovey and cute, our Mots Doux à ma Chérie JSK is the perfect clothing item for the occasion.

The JSK comes in a total of 4 colorways, 2 in dreamy pastel colors, and 2 in a bolder retro palette:

Pastel Colorways:

  • Late Bloomer (lavender)
  • Budding Feelings (mint)

Retro Colorways:

  • Midnight Dreamer (navy)
  • Blushing Blossom (light pink)

The JSK and skirt both have a side zipper, full back shirring for the perfect fit, and a hidden pocket. 

Our JSKs are made with 100% Cotton fabric (140gsm) and we cover a wide range of sizes, from a 69cm bust / 62cm waist (27.2 / 24.4 inch) up to a 140cm bust / 138cm waist (55.1 / 54.3 inch) 

This item is made by Fluffy Tori in Switzerland. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Knee Length Bloomers
description:
If you have never worn bloomers you are missing out! Bloomers are fabulous under skirts or dresses!
These Steampunk bloomers are a perfect comfortable and cute lounging outfit or PJs. They were first created in fashion history to be a ladies undergarments to be worn under fluffy dresses. 
They are fitted with soft elastic that is comfortable. The bottom also has elastic to keep cold air off your legs and keep them from creeping up your leg. Adorned with black satin ribbon.

Colors:
Black x White Damask (Shown)
Black Solid
White Solid


MAKE TIME:
Takes about 1-2 weeks to create and then are sent are priority mail domestic and international. International can be 1-4 weeks Domestic is 2-3 days.

Washing:
Machine wash and hang to dry.

-------------------------------------.

SIZES
Small-Waist 25-29
Medium-Waist 30-34
Large-Waist 35-39
XL-Waist 40-42
XXL-Waist 43-45
3X Waist 50-53
4X Waist 54-57
5X Waist 58-61


MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

-Measure right below your knee around your leg

How to Measure:
Basic:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kziKXUzxNSE

Advanced:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6eXvD7FfDE

---------------------------------

content:
If you have never worn bloomers you are missing out! Bloomers are fabulous under skirts or dresses!
These Steampunk bloomers are a perfect comfortable and cute lounging outfit or PJs. They were first created in fashion history to be a ladies undergarments to be worn under fluffy dresses. 
They are fitted with soft elastic that is comfortable. The bottom also has elastic to keep cold air off your legs and keep them from creeping up your leg. Adorned with black satin ribbon.

Colors:
Black x White Damask (Shown)
Black Solid
White Solid


MAKE TIME:
Takes about 1-2 weeks to create and then are sent are priority mail domestic and international. International can be 1-4 weeks Domestic is 2-3 days.

Washing:
Machine wash and hang to dry.

-------------------------------------.

SIZES
Small-Waist 25-29
Medium-Waist 30-34
Large-Waist 35-39
XL-Waist 40-42
XXL-Waist 43-45
3X Waist 50-53
4X Waist 54-57
5X Waist 58-61


MEASUREMENTS
**Use a soft measuring tape, this can be purchased at Joann’s or Michaels or even a general retail store

-Waist:
For the waist, measure the Natural waist which generally the smallest part of your torso or about an inch to 2 above your belly button.

-Measure right below your knee around your leg

How to Measure:
Basic:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kziKXUzxNSE

Advanced:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6eXvD7FfDE

---------------------------------

If you have any questions just message or e-mail me at info [!at] kmkdesigns.org


Photo by Nic Abrego

title: Lantern Sleeve Tie Back Blouse
description:
Lightweight and breathable, this Lantern Sleeve Tie Back Blouse by Sentaro is cool and comfortable! This semi-transparent blouse is available in fourteen beautiful colors and has a unique stand collar that ties in the back. Designed to be loose-fitting, it has elastic around the waist and wrists. 

Details:

  • Semi-transparent, lightweight material
  • Stand collar ties in the back
  • One size

Measurements: 

  • Bust: 80cm - 130cm
  • Waist: 60cm - 100cm
  • Upper Body Length: 43cm
  • Sleeve Length: 62cm


This item is made by Sentaro in China. It ships directly from the vendor. Please allow additional time for shipping.

title: Lavender Garden Jumperskirt Dress
description:
Welcome to the lavender garden, filled with the soothing scent. The delicately drawn lavender flowers will soothe your soul. This is a jumper skirt with light pleats on the chest and hem. The ladder lace and pre-tied ribbon on the shoulder straps add a cute touch.

The shirring at the back allows it to fit your body perfectly. An original print is applied to light domestic butcher fabric. The fine unevenness visible on the surface gives it a rich look. 

Details:

  • Back shirring
  • Adjustable shoulder straps
  • Pocket on right side of skirt
  • Inside is lined
  • Outer material: 100% polyester
  • Other material: 100% polyester
  • Lining: 100% polyester

Measurements: 

  • *Model height: 157cm [M size]
  • [ Size Plus] *Please note that this item sizing was made for Naka-Kon. As a result, the size chart for this is not available online, and these measurements are only estimates and are not exact.
  • Length: ~104cm
  • Bust: ~100 - 140cm
  • Waist: ~90 - 132 cm
  • Skirt length: ~62 cm

*Products are photographed using samples, and the color and specifications may differ slightly from the actual product depending on your monitor settings. Please note. 

This item is made by Melody BasKet in Japan. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Lovely Heart Gingham Cutsew Dress
description:
The Lovely Heart Gingham Cutsew Dress is the perfect mix of cute Lolita Fashion aesthetics, with the comfy-casual vibes of lounge wear. The bodice is made from a super soft jersey material, with a bit of stretch to allow you to move freely and comfortably while you go about your day. The lantern style sleeves are extra long (yes, even for gangly westerners!) to keep you feeling cozy and cute during those cooler months. The collar and bow on the front are both removable, so you can choose to wear this dress with both, or none, whatever suits your fancy! And, of course, we've got POCKETS! Two full size pockets, one on either side, to allow you to hold onto your phone, your snacks, your love letters - all the essentials!


Size 1 Measurements:
Bust: 96 cm
Waist: 76 cm
Sleeve Length: 60 cm
Total Length: 100 cm

Size 2 Measurements:
Bust: 125 cm
Waist: 110 cm
Sleeve Length: 63 cm
Total Length: 105 cm

Features:

  • Two full pockets
  • Removable Collar
  • Removable Bow
  • Side Zipper
  • Soft Jersey Bodice
  • Lantern Sleeve
  • Embroidered Collar

Item ships from our US Warehouse.

title: Map of a Fabled Land Button Down Shirt in Linen/Rayon
description:
It’s time to break out the short-sleeved shirts! Cottonbook has chosen a blend of linen for a classic summer texture and durability, and rayon, a wood-based fiber, for an added touch of softness and flow. This fabric brings textural interest to your look, and will slowly get softer with each wash.

This fantasy world full of mystical destinations, winding roads, and the creatures you might find was watercolor painted at my home studio in North Carolina.

Please check the size chart, in centimeters and flat measurements, to find your size. Runs large.

This item is made by Cottonbook in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Mary, Mary, Quite Contrary Skirt
description:
Mary, Mary, quite contrary, how does your garden grow?

This beautiful knee-length skirt is an homage to the classic nursery rhyme, which is also embroidered onto the lacy front pocket. The body of the skirt is covered in colorful floral embroidery, much like a moving garden. 

The outer fabric is a soft, swishy mesh which is slightly sheer. Beneath it is a full cotton lining for breathability and comfort.  

The waistband is half-elastic, making the fit stretchy and accommodating. It also has pockets at both side seams!

These photos show the skirt over a petticoat to show off the full volume. You can also wear it without a petticoat for a softer, more casual silhouette. 

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: self fabric- 50% cotton, 50% polyester. Lining- 100% cotton. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold on gentle cycle, lay flat to dry

 

Size Chart

 Size Waist
XS 25"-28"
S 28"-32"
M 32"-36"
L 36"-42"
1X 40"-46"
2X 44"-50"
3X 48"-54"
4X 52"-58"

These measurements are recommended body measurements. Choose the size closest to your actual measurements. The waistband is fully elastic with lots of stretch. All measurements in inches.

This item is made by Atelier Heidi. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Pastel Colored Clown Cardigan
description:
It’s always sweater weather when you have body dysmorphia! Okay but let’s be real, these cardigans are designed to be a hug just like from a comfy knit blanket. Each cardigan is designed to be as sensory friendly as possible. The material is made from 100% Cotton that is hand dyed to match the designated color. Both the material and that the knit is heavier than average is designed to help anyone with sensory issues. But the most important part is that all tags are in the front left pocket to avoid any unnecessary tag contact. Don’t be surprised if your friends or partner(s) want to borrow it since it’s just so cozy. 

This cardi can be the perfect addition to your wardrobe! It can be worn both super every day outfits, or dressed up with the perfect collared blouse, skirt or whatever you plan to coord it with! 

The Carigans are available in 5 sizes: XS, Small-medium, Large-XL, 2XL-3XL, 4XL-5XL. Each size is designed to fit loose or oversized with the following US Standard measurements. They are also designed with longer than average arm length to accommodate taller folks (yay!)

    ***Note about sizing: after initial production we received feedback stating that the 4/6XL is not true to size to fit a 6XL. Going forward all marketing of this size will state 4/5XL, however the tag still indicates “6XL”. The measurements are still the same, we are just no longer marketing this size as 6XL going forward***

note: model is wearing the large/xl

 

This item is made by Egglien Creations in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

content:
This outfit is great for parties, Halloween, and costume events, it's so comfy to wear! It can even be a fun conversational outfit you wear out and about! This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waists for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with a two black button in the back.

TOP: Short cream chemise top
PETTICOAT: black base with orange tulle
MASK: matching fitted mask

Make time: Takes about 3-4 weeks to be made and then is shipped Priority mail domestic which takes about 2-3 days and priority international which takes 6-10 days but can vary up to a month depending on the country. Shipping Upgrade available message us for details. Washing: Machine wash and hang to dry. ============================

title: Puppy Witch Party Skirt - Green
description:
This is our new Design, Puppy Witch Party!
This is a single layer skirt, so lighter than many of our other design.

The print is adorable, as as usual 2 pockets are included.

This design comes in multiple colorways, but stock is limited at the moment.

For this design we have 2 sizes available right now
The Elastic is quite strong and able to fit a wide range of waist sizes. So far during the test fit the models said they were comfortable.

S-L: For Waist: 60cm-100cm (23.6inch- 39.3inch)

Xl-5XL: For Waist: 100cm-150cm (39.3inch-59inch)

This item is made by Night Whisper in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Purple Flower Bloomers
description:
Adorable cotton shorts with a ruffled, knee-length hem. The bottom hem has a drawstring which you can tighten for a gathered look, or loosen for a straight cut. An elastic waistband provides a comfortable, versatile fit. They also have pockets!

These are cool and breathable, making them perfect for summer! Wear them on their own as shorts, or layered under a dress or tunic top.

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: 100% cotton. Imported.
Care instructions: Gentle machine wash and tumble dry low

Model is 5'7" and wearing size M.

title: Rabbit Card Jumperskirt Dress
description:
Write your feelings for her on a card with cute flowers. A seasonal message delivered by a fluffy rabbit.

This is a jumper skirt with a waist ribbon as a highlight. You can also wear it simply by removing the ribbon. The shoulder straps are decorated with delicate lace flowers, giving it a flawless cuteness. The back is partially shirred with elastic to fit your body.

Made from domestic butcher fabric with a fine, uneven texture and an expressive feel. It has an original print. It is light and smooth against the skin.

Adjustable shoulder straps. Comes with a pocket on the right side of the skirt. Made in Japan.

Details:

  • Partial ack shirring
  • Adjustable shoulder straps
  • Pocket on right side of skirt
  • Inside is lined
  • Outer material: 100% polyester
  • Other material: 100% polyester
  • Lining: 100% polyester

Measurements: 

  • *Model height: 157cm [M size]
  • [ Size Plus] *Please note that this item sizing was made for Naka-Kon. As a result, the size chart for this is not available online, and these measurements are only estimates and are not exact.
  • Length: ~104cm
  • Bust: ~100 - 140cm
  • Waist: ~90 - 132 cm
  • Skirt length: ~62 cm

*Products are photographed using samples, and the color and specifications may differ slightly from the actual product depending on your monitor settings. Please note. 

This item is made by Melody BasKet in Japan. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Rainbow Parade Jumperskirt
description:
Join the parade!

Our Rainbow Parade collection celebrates diversity in all of its shapes and forms – love yourself and live the kawaii life of your dreams, not despite being "different", but because of the beauty of it!

Our JSKs are made from Ecocert Organic Cotton (Organic Cotton Twill Poplin Fabric 100% Cotton, 140gsm, OEKO-TEX 100 Standard) and we cover a wide range of sizes, from a 69 cm bust/62 cm waist (27.2/24.4 inch) up to a 140 cm bust/138 cm waist (55.1/54.3 inch). The JSK has a full elastic back shirring to be the comfiest of all!

The JSK has a removable rainbow stripe belt. And, of course, like all Fluffy Tori dresses, they have 2 pockets! (and they are rainbow!) The photos show our JSK sample in the rainbow colorway. The final version will have some minor changes, including adjustable straps that actually have stripes in all colors of the rainbow as well as a different bodice decor, as shown in the mockup (larger crystal heart buttons and a removable fabric strip that is white on one side, lavender on the other). 

This item is made by Fluffy Tori in Switzerland. It ships from our US warehouse

title: Rainbow Petticoat
description:
This is our 6th release version, regular size will be poofer than the 5th release. We also added new length.

Double-Sided Rainbow Tutu Petticoat
Authentic brand: Kolest

Super super super soft and comfy!

Size suggestions:
Our elastic can extend very large! Measure your natural waist and find your size down below:

Short Length=18" (45cm）
Long Length = 22" (55cm)

Size M, Suggest for natural waist 24"- 39" (60-100cm)

Size XL, Suggest for natural waist 35.5"- 59" (90-150cm)


----------------------------------------


Fabric Safety: the fabric passed all safety tests, NO AZO dyes, NO formaldehyde.

❤ Be aware, this is a registered patent design in China. Our partner brand Kolest owns this design. Any this design Rainbow Tutu Skirt not from this brand is considered as copy. Thanks for supporting our designers!!!

How to find if the rainbow petticoat is from the original designer:
1. The rainbow petticoat can be worn two sides, their stitches are excellent. Other copies don't have the same quality stitches, also can't wear two sides.
2. The petticoat has brand tag Kolest as shown in the photo.

title: Rococo Jumperskirt
description:
Rococo Sweet Lolita Jumper JSK Kawaii Clothing Marie Antoinette Cosplay Dress Blue Cotton Custom Petite to Plus Size

Like Marie Antoinette? Like to eat cake? The rococo sweet lolita jumper may be for you!
This Lolita JSK can be made petite to plus, it is a fun new take on the Kawaii Japanese Fashion mixed with the KMK Style. Perfect for a Cosplay dress at a convention or event. Make a cute blue and cream rococo lolita cord with this jumper!
Be fashionable and adorable in this custom JSK.
This style is called "Rococo Jumper"

This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waist for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with two white buttons in the back.

Make time:
Will take up to 2-3 weeks in our schedule to make and ship to you. Shipped Priority which takes 2-3 days domestic and 1-6 weeks international varies by country.
For international please give yourself a 4 week delivery time on top of the make time. Some countries there is a faster delivery please inquire. There is also shipping upgrades available.

Washing:
Dry cleaned or hand washed
_______________________________
SIZES

Sizes Natural waist about an inch above your belly button
Small-Waist 25-29
Medium-Waist 30-34
Large-Waist 35-39
XL-Waist 40-42
XXL-Waist 43-45
3X Waist 46-48
4X Waist 49-51
5X 52-54

Length is about 22-24 inches from your waist please include a specific length from your waist if you have a preference.

Meant to be worn with a petticoat, but can be worn without. Can't be worn without a blouse.

How to Measure:
Basic:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kziKXUzxNSE

Advanced:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6eXvD7FfDE

title: Rose Garden Dress
description:
An elegant gown with a blooming rose print, adorned with lots of lace and delicate details.

This is made in the style of a Classic Lolita jumperskirt, with an elastic back panel and adjustable shoulder straps. It ties at the waist with a removable sash, and the skirt is full and flowing. Wear it with or without a petticoat for your desired silhouette.

This dress comes with a convertible bow, which has both a fabric pin and a hair clip on the back side. It's very easy to remove or reposition the bow according to your tastes!

Matching Rose Garden Wrist Cuffs and Rose Garden Headdresses are sold separately.

The main material is 100% cotton, including the lining. The sheer lace overlay is synthetic.

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: cotton, some synthetic lace. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang to dry

 

Size Chart

Size Bust Waist
XS 31"-34" 26"-30"
S 34"-36" 30"-34"
M 36"-38" 34"-36"
L 38"-42" 36"-42"
1X 42"-44" 40"-46"
2X 44"-48" 44"-50"
3X 48"-54" 48"-54"
4X 52"-56" 52"-58"

These measurements are recommended body measurements. Choose the size closest to your actual measurements. The actual garment is slightly larger to account for wearing ease. This waistband is elastic and can accommodate a slightly larger size, and it can also be tied down to a smaller size. All measurements in inches.

This item is made by Atelier Heidi in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

This is made in the style of a Classic Lolita jumperskirt, with an elastic back panel and adjustable shoulder straps. It ties at the waist with a removable sash, and the skirt is full and flowing. Wear it with or without a petticoat for your desired silhouette.

This dress comes with a convertible bow, which has both a fabric pin and a hair clip on the back side. It's very easy to remove or reposition the bow according to your tastes!

Matching Rose Garden Wrist Cuffs and Rose Garden Headdresses are sold separately.

The main material is 100% cotton, including the lining. The sheer lace overlay is synthetic.

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: cotton, some synthetic lace. Made in China.
Care: machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang to dry

 

Size Chart

Size Bust Waist
XS 31"-34" 26"-30"
S 34"-36" 30"-34"
M 36"-38" 34"-36"
L 38"-42" 36"-42"
1X 42"-44" 40"-46"
2X 44"-48" 44"-50"
3X 48"-54" 48"-54"
4X 52"-56" 52"-58"

These measurements are recommended body measurements. Choose the size closest to your actual measurements. The actual garment is slightly larger to account for wearing ease. This waistband is elastic and can accommodate a slightly larger size, and it can also be tied down to a smaller size. All measurements in inches.

This item is made by Atelier Heidi in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Shoujo Leopard Jumperskirt
description:
Mahou Shoujo Power!

Ready to fight crime and look cute doing it? PreOrders for Magical Mews' first dress Shoujo Leopard are here! Inspired by old school punk lolita and gyaru fashion this dress gives such nostalgic vibes.

Featuring a sweetheart top adorned with crossing neck straps, faux lace up and sweet little heart buttons flatter the printed design. Printed design is an all over leopard style pattern with little hearts and magic shoujo bubbles. Structure of the dress is a lovely three tier that gives a beautiful cupcake or a line shape worn with either style of petticoat. Colors range from a bright pink coral, pink and light pink.

Photos are taken in several types of light from cool to more warm to see differences in look. As well as as two different size dress forms. Model is wearing Size 2. Height 5' and weight 185 with room to spare.

Details:

  • Dress has 2 pockets.
  • Shirring in back to fit multiple sizes.
  • Adjustable straps to wear easily.
  • Please do note that the length of the dress will be on the shorter side. The model featured is 5ft.

Size 1: Bust 80-100 cm, Waist 70-90 cm
Size 2: Bust 100-120 cm, Waist 80-100 cm
Size 3: Bust 117-140 cm, Waist 100-125 cm

This item is a In Stock by Magical Mews from Missouri. It will ship from our warehouse in Kansas City, Missouri.

title: Skirt - Mots Doux à ma Chérie
description:
Mots Doux à ma Chérie is our collection for true romantics that combines shōwa era manga style, vintage Valentine's aesthetics, and a sakura theme, resulting in a sweet-as-candy romantic retro print.

Whether you are going on a Valentine's day date, having a cherry blossom picnic or simply feeling all lovey-dovey and cute, our Mots Doux à ma Chérie Skirt is the perfect clothing item for the occasion.

The skirt comes in a total of 4 colorways, 2 in dreamy pastel colors, and 2 in a bolder retro palette:

Pastel Colorways:

  • Late Bloomer (lavender)
  • Budding Feelings (mint)

Retro Colorways:

  • Midnight Dreamer (navy)
  • Blushing Blossom (light pink)

The JSK and skirt both have a side zipper, full back shirring for the perfect fit, and a hidden pocket. 

For sizing please look at the attached image of our size chart.

This item is made by Fluffy Tori in Switzerland. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Slime Cardigan
description:
It’s always sweater weather when you have body dysmorphia! Okay but let’s be real, these cardigans are designed to be a hug just like from a comfy knit blanket. Each cardigan is designed to be as sensory friendly as possible. The material is made from 100% Cotton that is hand dyed to match the designated color. Both the material and that the knit is heavier than average is designed to help anyone with sensory issues. But the most important part is that all tags are in the front left pocket to avoid any unnecessary tag contact. Don’t be surprised if your friends or partner(s) want to borrow it since it’s just so cozy. 

This cardi can be the perfect addition to your wardrobe! It can be worn both super every day outfits, or dressed up with the perfect collared blouse, skirt or whatever you plan to coord it with! 

The Carigans are available in 5 sizes: XS, Small-medium, Large-XL, 2XL-3XL, 4XL-5XL. Each size is designed to fit loose or oversized with the following US Standard measurements. They are also designed with longer than average arm length to accommodate taller folks (yay!)

    ***Note about sizing: after initial production we received feedback stating that the 4/6XL is not true to size to fit a 6XL. Going forward all marketing of this size will state 4/5XL, however the tag still indicates “6XL”. The measurements are still the same, we are just no longer marketing this size as 6XL going forward***

note: model is wearing the large/XL

 

This item is made by Egglien Creations in the USA. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Solid Velvet Skirt
description:
❧ 𝓐𝓬𝓽 𝓘 - 𝓐 𝓡𝓸𝓼𝓮 𝓢𝓬𝓮𝓷𝓽𝓮𝓭 𝓡𝓸𝓶𝓪𝓷𝓬𝓮

Back in the gold days of sad poetesses and drunk painters, when the streets where wet and the fog was dense, a tiny café was the brighter place around. Café Rosé was old and shabby and the colored light of the stained glass windows blended in harmony with the hundreds of varieties of roses and peonies that filled the room.

title: Triple M's Onepiece Dress
description:
"Midori Fukasawa x Misako Aoki x Melody BasKet" Triple collaboration
The dream of a triple collaboration has come true!
A special dress has been created by popular lolita models Midori Fukasawa and Misako Aoki (aka “Midomisa”) ♥"

Topped with ruffles, ribbons, and original lace, the voluminous skirt bounces with every movement, making your heart bounce ♪ The open collar beautifully shows off your neck, the sleeve length makes your arms look delicate, and the length is cute and mature.

This is a special piece that shows attention to detail. A generous amount of fabric is used. Each color gives a different impression.

[Fabric used]
Pink, Sax: Satin Seersucker
A seersucker fabric with a soft gingham check pattern with a slight sheerness. It is characterized by its uneven texture.

Red: Lawn Gingham
A thin gingham check lawn fabric made with thin and delicate threads. It is an elegant material that is smooth to the touch.

Gray: Spun Twill
Thin twill fabric with a natural texture. It has a soft texture that feels like it has just been washed.

Details: 

  • Removable ribbon at back
  • Back zipper closure
  • Elastic at back of waist
  • Elastic cuff shirring
  • Pocket on right side of skirt
  • Outer material (pink, saxe, gray): 100% polyester
  • Outer material (red): 100% cotton
  • Other material: 100% polyester
  • Lining: 100% polyester

Measurements:

  • [ Size M ]
  • Length: 112 cm
  • Bust: 94.2cm
  • Waist: 76 - 80cm
  • Shoulder Width: 35cm
  • Sleeve Length: 34cm + 6.5cm lace
  • Cuffs: 25cm
  • Skirt length: 74cm

 

  • [ Size L ]
  • Length: 118cm
  • Bust: 100.2cm
  • Waist: 82 - 86cm
  • Shoulder Width: 38cm
  • Sleeve Length: 35.5cm + 6.5cm lace
  • Cuffs: 26cm
  • Skirt length: 78cm

 

  • [ Size Plus ]
  • Length:  116cm
  • Bust: 124cm
  • Waist: 103 - 109cm
  • Shoulder Width: 43cm
  • Sleeve Length: 37cm + 6.5cm lace
  • Cuffs: 29cm
  • Skirt length: 74cm

This item is made by Melody BasKet in Japan. It ships from our US warehouse.

title: Velveteen Rabbit Pinafore
description:
This soft and comfy pinafore is themed after the classic story The Velveteen Rabbit. Made from cotton velveteen, it features custom embroidered artwork and adorable bunny lace! The front pocket includes a quote from the story about becoming Real.

This pinafore has two pockets at the side seams and one decorative front pocket. The straps are adjustable with buttons, and it opens at the sides with buttons for easy dressing. 

The brown/mauve colorway is photographed over petticoat for a more dramatic shape. The other two colorways are pictured without the petticoat. Wear it with or without a petticoat for your desired silhouette.

Brand: Atelier Heidi
Materials: 100% cotton. Made in China.

title: Wide Calf Radiant Rainbow Stripes Knee High Socks
description:
For our Stripes series it was only a matter of time until "black and a color" became "black and ALL colors," or at least five of them! Rainbows are the perfect fit for stripes, and these socks bear a repeating pattern of red, yellow, green, blue, and purple. The black stripes between each color are how you know it's a Gothic rainbow. Black also makes the colors brighter in contrast, which is why it's important to have darkness in your life. These are our wide calf version of this design and they fit calves up to 23 inches around.

In order to maintain the vibrancy of the color, this sock was sewn with a white elastic base. This may show through the stripes when the socks are stretched, but should not noticeably affect the design.

------

Sock Specs:

  • Combed Cotton/Nylon/Spandex for breathability, durability, and stretch
  • DOUBLE TERRY in the heel and toe area adds durability and comfort where most novelty sock brands fail.
  • 200N Thread Count for highest level of detail
  • 40 Gram Socks with smooth seams
  • No uncomfortable bumps in the toe area
  • One Size Fits Most Humans Size 6-13 with Calves up to 23 Inches Around

This product ships from our partner, FootClothes, in the USA.

title: Witch Dress High Waisted Jumperskirt
description:
Witch Dress High Waisted Jumper Skirt Goth Kawaii Gothic Lolita JSK with Bustle Pulls Petite to Plus Size Custom to Order

This Gothic jumper dress is inspired by Gothic Lolita Japanese fashion. This jumper has adjustable bustle pull in the front, take may it even more versatile and fun! This Gothic Jumper dress is great for an adult Halloween costume that you can work into your everyday wardrobe adding some gothy Tim Burton fun! Works for a witchy fashion look, a goth doll inspired look or a Tim Burton inspired outfit!
This style is called out "Goth bow Jumper".
This Jumper is made with multiple elastic waist for a snug fit. It zips up in the back with a zipper and the straps have three adjustable lengths, adjustable with two buttons in the back.

WANT THE WHOLE LOOK?
